### 2. Document Structure Requirements
- **DOCTYPE**: Always use `<!DOCTYPE html>`
- **Language**: Include `lang="en"` on html element
- **Viewport**: Include responsive viewport meta tag
- **Charset**: Use UTF-8 encoding
- **Title**: Descriptive, unique page titles

